title: New Zealand Consumer Spending
description: Consumer Spending in New Zealand decreased to 43264 NZD Million in the second quarter of 2022 from 44633 NZD Million in the first quarter of 2022. Consumer Spending in New Zealand averaged 25855.89 NZD Million from 1987 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 44633 NZD Million in the first quarter of 2022 and a record low of 15062 NZD Million in the second quarter of 1987. This page provides the latest reported value for - New Zealand Consumer Spending - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Statistics New Zealand
